# Screenshots Directory

Add the following screenshots:

1. `banner.png` - A wide banner image for the README header (optional)
2. `path-screen.png` - The learning path view showing timeline and nodes
3. `study-screen.png` - The study screen with Mishnah text and explanation
4. `quiz-screen.png` - The quiz screen with a question

Recommended dimensions:
- Banner: 1200x400px
- Screenshots: 390x844px (iPhone 14 Pro dimensions)

To take screenshots:
1. Open https://halomed.vercel.app/ on mobile or in Chrome DevTools mobile view
2. Navigate to each screen
3. Take screenshots and save them here
